fields.name: ReportUrl
fields.description: Sas url to the async benefit utilization summaries report. Will be empty if the report is in Running or Failed state.

fields.name: SecondaryReportUrl
fields.description: Sas url to async benefit utilization summaries report in secondary storage in case of primary outage. Will be empty if the report is in Running or Failed state.

fields.name: ValidUntil
fields.description: The date that the sas url provided in reportUrl expires.
